03:15.520 --> 03:17.190
Tiada masalah, terima kasih.

03:17.190 --> 03:18.130
Minum dulu.

03:22.680 --> 03:23.590
-Tuan Shen.
-Tuan Shen.

03:23.590 --> 03:24.530
